Detailed Description

Structure used to disable or enable the range mapping and range reduction feature and also it defines the range mapping values for Y and UV component.

struct Vps_RngMapRdtCfg

Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_RngMapRdtCfg::rngMapEnable

[IN] Defines whether to enable or disable the range mapping feature.

UInt32 Vps_RngMapRdtCfg::rngMapValUV

[IN] Defines the range mapping value for UV component For valid values see Vps_RngMapVal.

UInt32 Vps_RngMapRdtCfg::rngMapValY

[IN] Defines the range mapping value for Y component For valid values see Vps_RngMapVal.

UInt32 Vps_RngMapRdtCfg::rngRdtEnable

[IN] Defines whether to enable or disable the range reduction feature.
